General.Name: Power REIT
General.Description: Power REIT, with a focus on the "Triple Bottom Line" and a commitment to Profit, Planet and People is a specialized real estate investment trust (REIT) that owns sustainable real estate related to infrastructure assets including properties for Controlled Environment Agriculture, Renewable Energy and Transportation. Power REIT is actively seeking to expand its real estate portfolio related to Controlled Environment Agriculture in the form of greenhouses for the cultivation of food and cannabis.
General.Address: 301 Winding Road, Old Bethpage, NY, United States, 11804
